    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring light back to the darkening town of Mallard by exploring its monster-infested outskirts, hearing its residents' stories, and defeating the dangerous pets of a mastermind light-stealer in this simple top-down adventure inspired by a love of exploring one's own neighborhood. Features several unique items that can be used to navigate the world and defend yourself from monsters, fun and emotionally deep interactions with the residents of Mallard, and a large cast of wacky monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game takes 3-4 hours to complete. Replay the game to find different routes. </p>",
